root: ^Nannan: Shortly after, the Warlock moved into my home. He claimed to know magic that could cure my brother, who had been sick for a long time, so my parents were eager to have him stay.
^Nannan: Rumor has it that the Warlock was chased away from our village back when he was a student, but no one knows why.
^Nannan: Why is he back? What does he want from my family?
